vir)." AbbVie US LLC, North Chicago, IL.[2] "Product Information. Norvir (ritonavir)." Abbott Pharmaceutical, Abbott Park, IL.[3] "Product Information. Viekira Pak (dasabuvir/ombitasvir/paritaprevir/ritonavir)." AbbVie US LLC, North Chicago, IL.[4] Schubert W, Eriksson U, Edgar B, Cullberg G, Hedner T "Flavonoids in grapefruit juice inhibit the in vitro hepatic metabolism of 17B-estradiol." Eur J Drug Metab Pharmacokinet 20 (1995): 219-24[5] Weber A, Jager R, Borner A, et al. "Can grapefruit juice influence ethinyl estradiol bioavailability?" Contraception 53 (1996): 41-7', 1767363023);
