"APPGuide online. Australian prescription products guide online. Available from: URL: http://www.appco.com.au/appguide/default.asp." ([2006]):[19] Schaferkorting M "Pharmacokinetic optimisation of oral antifungal therapy." Clin Pharmacokinet 25 (1993): 329-41', 1767363023);
